These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-1::.
Movie-Genre: horror, western, documentary, fantasy
Pet: dog, goat, horse, mouse
1. Pet:mouse is on the left of Movie-Genre:documentary##1
2. Movie-Genre:horror is on the left of Pet:goat##1
3. Movie-Genre:fantasy is in an odd position##4
4. Pet:horse is on the left or right of Pet:mouse##3
5. Movie-Genre:horror is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |  1  |   2    |   3   |    4     |
| Movie-Genre   | horror | western | fantasy | documentary |
| Pet        | dog | goat   | mouse | horse    |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-2::.
Movie-Genre: crime, musical, scientific, superhero
Job: analyst, social-worker, project-manager, entrepreneur
1. Movie-Genre:musical is on the left of Movie-Genre:superhero##1
2. Job:analyst is on the left of Job:project-manager##1
3. Job:project-manager is in an odd position##4
4. Job:analyst == Movie-Genre:crime##1
5. Job:social-worker is on the right of Job:project-manager##1
6. Job:analyst == Movie-Genre:crime##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |   2    |    3     |     4     |
| Movie-Genre   | scientific | crime  | musical  | superhero |
| Job   | entrepreneur    | analyst | project-manager | social-worker    |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-3::.
Food: carrot, grapes, pomegranate, watermelon
House: townhouse, wooden, cape-cod, ranch-style
1. Food:watermelon is on the left or right of House:ranch-style##3
2. Food:pomegranate is in an even position##4
3. House:ranch-style is on the left or right of Food:grapes##3
4. House:ranch-style is on the right of House:cape-cod##1
5. House:townhouse is in an odd position##4
6. Food:grapes is on the right of Food:pomegranate##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |     3     |      4      |
| Food          | watermelon | pomegranate | grapes    | carrot      |
| House   | cape-cod        | ranch-style     | townhouse | wooden |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-4::.
Flower: sunflower, amaryllis, aconite, balloon-flower
Music-Genre: blues, folk, indie, reggae
1. Flower:amaryllis is between Music-Genre:blues and Music-Genre:reggae##2
2. Flower:balloon-flower is on the left of Flower:sunflower##1
3. Music-Genre:indie is in an odd position##4
4. Music-Genre:folk is on the left of Music-Genre:reggae##1
5. Music-Genre:folk is on the right of Flower:sunflower##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |    3    |    4    |
| Flower         | balloon-flower | sunflower | amaryllis | aconite |
| Music-Genre   | indie       | blues   | folk    | reggae  |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-5::.
Music-Genre: folk, hip-hop, jazz, punk
Color: black, fuchsia, chestnut, mauve
1. Music-Genre:jazz is on the right of Color:mauve##1
2. Color:fuchsia == Music-Genre:punk##1
3. Color:chestnut is on the right of Music-Genre:folk##1
4. Music-Genre:hip-hop is on the far left##1
5. Music-Genre:jazz is in an odd position##4
6. Color:black is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |   3    |     4      |
| Music-Genre   | hip-hop  | folk    | jazz   | punk       |
| Color   | black | mauve | chestnut | fuchsia |

