2. Transport:roller is on the left of Transport:car##1
3. Cigar:swisher is on the left of Cigar:dunhill##1
4. Transport:ship == Cigar:bongani##1
5. Cigar:swisher is on the left or right of Transport:car##3
6. Transport:quad-bike is on the right of Transport:car##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |    2    |    3    |     4     |
| Cigar   | bongani | swisher | dunhill | game    |
| Transport     | ship | roller  | car     | quad-bike |

