2. House:cape-cod is in an odd position##4
3. Pet:guinea-pig is on the left or right of House:cape-cod##3
4. House:cape-cod is on the right of Pet:guinea-pig##1
5. House:townhouse is between House:cape-cod and House:colonial##2
6. Pet:fish is in an odd position##4
7. Pet:fish is between House:townhouse and Pet:goat##2
8. House:townhouse is on the left or right of House:colonial##3

.:: Answer ::.
|       |   1   |     2      |    3    |        4        |
| House   | colonial | townhouse      | cape-cod | art-deco |
