.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-10::.
Beverage: almond-milk, cola, juice, soy-milk
House: art-deco, palace, victorian, craftsman
1. Beverage:almond-milk == House:craftsman##1
2. House:art-deco is on the right of Beverage:almond-milk##1
3. House:craftsman is between House:art-deco and Beverage:juice##2
4. Beverage:almond-milk is in an odd position##4
5. House:craftsman is on the left or right of House:art-deco##3
6. Beverage:cola is on the left or right of House:palace##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2    |      3      |    4     |
| Beverage      | cola       | juice   | almond-milk | soy-milk |
| House   | victorian | palace | craftsman        | art-deco    |

