.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-17::.
City: london, berlin, venice, nizza
Nationality: american, japanese, nigerian, turkish
1. City:venice is on the left of City:london##1
2. City:venice is in an even position##4
3. Nationality:japanese == City:venice##1
4. Nationality:nigerian is on the left or right of Nationality:japanese##3
5. Nationality:japanese is between Nationality:turkish and Nationality:nigerian##2
6. City:berlin is on the right of Nationality:turkish##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |      3      |    4     |
| City         | nizza   | venice | london | berlin    |
| Nationality   | nigerian | japanese  | turkish     | american |

