.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-18::.
Beverage: 7up, fanta, milk, water
Hobby: collecting, camping, video-games, drawing
1. Hobby:camping is on the far left##1
2. Beverage:milk is on the left or right of Beverage:7up##3
3. Beverage:water is on the far left or far right##3
4. Hobby:video-games is on the left of Hobby:drawing##1
5. Hobby:drawing is on the right of Beverage:7up##1
6. Hobby:video-games is in an even position##4
7. Hobby:collecting == Beverage:fanta##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1   |   2    |     3      |   4   |
| Beverage   | water | 7up    | milk       | fanta |
| Hobby       | camping  | video-games | drawing | collecting  |

