.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-20::.
Job: entrepreneur, manager, pilot, software-developer
City: colone, hannover, new-york, london
1. Job:manager is in an even position##4
2. Job:manager is on the left or right of City:colone##3
3. City:hannover is between Job:entrepreneur and City:colone##2
4. Job:manager is on the far left or far right##3
5. City:new-york is on the right of Job:software-developer##1
6. City:new-york is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1       |    2    |         3          |    4    |
| Job         | entrepreneur | pilot   | software-developer | manager |
| City   | london          | hannover | colone         | new-york  |

 